</para>
</refsect1>

<refsect1>
<title>Examples</title>
<programlisting>
MaxClientsPerHost 1 &quot;Sorry, you may not connect more than one time.&quot;
Results in: 530 Sorry, you may not connect more than one time.
</programlisting>
